    <li>Improved the Webasyst 2 interface and added various minor conveniences.</li> 
    <li>Improved navigation in the <em>Plugins</em> section’s content.</li> 
    <li>Improved support for the latest PHP versions.</li> 
    <li>Fixed found errors.</li> 
</ul>";s:8:"datetime";s:19:"2024-11-06 15:33:24";}i:1;a:3:{s:7:"version";s:11:"11.0.0.1021";s:7:"content";s:2682:"<ul>
    <li>Convenient work with <strong>mobile POS terminals </strong>and centralized <strong>payments fiscalization control</strong> for processing offline orders:
        <ul>
            <li>new<em> POS</em> section in the <em>mobile Shop-Script app</em> for Android and iOS,</li>
            <li>additional filter for orders with payment via a mobile POS terminal,</li>
            <li>order action<em> initiate POS payment</em>, which is available for such orders,</li>
            <li>new settings section <em>POS</em> with a quick search for fiscalization-enabled plugins.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Added support for product videos from the <em>VK Video</em> service.</li>
    <li>Improved new Webasyst 2 user interface.</li>
    <li>Other improvements &amp; bug fixes:
        <ul>
            <li>description of method <em>$wa-&gt;shop-&gt;getListThumbsTemplate()</em> added to the design editor cheat sheet to facilitate publishing product sets in the storefront,</li>
            <li>uploading images in the info page editor,</li>
            <li>error in the <em>Reports → Products</em> section,</li>
            <li>execution of CRON command <em>searchIndex</em>.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Enhanced API methods for developers:
        <ul>
            <li>new method <em>shop.coupon.getInfo</em> to obtain information about a discount coupon,</li>
            <li>new method <em>shop.coupon.getList</em> to obtain information about several coupons,</li>
            <li>new method <em>shop.order.addSale</em> to create basic sales orders with optional customer details,</li>
            <li>new method <em>shop.settings.getProductCodes</em> to obtain information about setup product codes,</li>
            <li>new method <em>shop.settings.getShippingTypes</em> to obtain information about enabled shipping methods,</li>
            <li>new method <em>shop.settings.getStockUnits</em> to obtain information about setup product quantity units,</li>
            <li>in method <em>shop.order.search</em> added the option to obtain information about ordered products’ quantity units,</li>
            <li>in method <em>shop.settings.getPaymentTypes</em> added parameter <em>pos</em> to obtain only the payment methods allowing payments via a mobile POS terminal or by a QR code,</li>
            <li>in methods <em>shop.order.add</em>, <em>shop.order.save</em>, <em>shop.order.saveItem</em> added the option to specify product codes as part of the <em>items</em> parameter,</li>
            <li>improved descriptions of API methods for testing in the <em>API Explorer</em> app.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>";s:8:"datetime";s:19:"2024-09-24 10:41:01";}}s:9:"purchased";s:0:"";s:9:"beta_test";b:0;s:7:"inbuilt";b:0;s:7:"plugins";a:1:{s:9:"ordercall";a:12:{s:4:"name";s:22:"shop/plugins/ordercall";s:6:"vendor";i:934303;s:4:"icon";s:81:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/31/2731/icon.en_US.png?v=1.19.0";s:5:"icons";a:1:{i:200;s:80:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/31/2731/icon.200x110.en_US.png";}s:10:"commercial";b:1;s:7:"version";s:6:"1.19.0";s:15:"update_datetime";s:19:"2024-09-23 17:04:52";s:12:"download_url";s:77:"https://updates.webasyst.com/download/archive/wa-apps/shop/plugins/ordercall/";s:12:"requirements";a:0:{}s:9:"purchased";s:0:"";s:9:"beta_test";b:0;s:7:"inbuilt";b:0;}}}s:4:"site";a:13:{s:4:"name";s:4:"Site";s:6:"vendor";s:8:"webasyst";s:4:"icon";s:77:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/32/132/icon.png?v=3.0.0.321";s:5:"icons";a:4:{i:96;s:71:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/32/132/icon.96x96.png";i:48;s:71:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/32/132/icon.48x48.png";i:24;s:71:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/32/132/icon.24x24.png";i:16;s:71:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/32/132/icon.16x16.png";}s:10:"commercial";b:0;s:7:"version";s:9:"3.0.0.321";s:15:"update_datetime";s:19:"2024-11-20 11:48:50";s:12:"download_url";s:59:"https://updates.webasyst.com/download/archive/wa-apps/site/";s:12:"requirements";a:2:{s:3:"php";a:2:{s:6:"strict";b:1;s:7:"version";s:8:">=7.4.24";}s:13:"app.installer";a:2:{s:7:"version";s:11:">=3.4.0.944";s:6:"strict";b:1;}}s:9:"changelog";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:7:"version";s:9:"3.0.0.321";s:7:"content";s:1104:"<ul>
    <li>Major update: support for the <strong>Webasyst 2</strong> interface, new <strong>Site map</strong> section, <strong>custom variables</strong>, and many minor improvements.
        <ul>
            <li>The <em>Site map</em> is a new unified interface for managing the site’s structure and pages. It has been designed to conveniently configure all site sections and pages, easily select a homepage and add new pages, set up the personal account for your clients as well as redirecting rules.</li>
            <li><em>Переменные</em> are small portions of text that you may need to publish across your entire website such as a phone number or your YouTube channel name. To change such a snippet on all site pages, you only need to modify one variable in the settings.</li>
            <li>Various improvements: added a main page with the list of all your sites and small preview thumbnails of their homepages, canceled the requirement to add an asterisk at the end of each site section address, and added plenty of other convenient tweaks.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>";s:8:"datetime";s:19:"2024-11-20 11:48:51";}}s:9:"purchased";b:1;s:9:"beta_test";b:0;s:7:"inbuilt";b:0;}s:4:"team";a:13:{s:4:"name";s:4:"Team";s:6:"vendor";s:8:"webasyst";s:4:"icon";s:78:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/88/2588/icon.png?v=2.3.3.240";s:5:"icons";a:4:{i:96;s:72:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/88/2588/icon.96x96.png";i:48;s:72:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/88/2588/icon.48x48.png";i:24;s:72:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/88/2588/icon.24x24.png";i:16;s:72:"//updates.webasyst.com/wa-data/public/updates/img/88/2588/icon.16x16.png";}s:10:"commercial";b:0;s:7:"version";s:9:"2.3.3.240";s:15:"update_datetime";s:19:"2024-11-06 15:34:06";s:12:"download_url";s:59:"https://updates.webasyst.com/download/archive/wa-apps/team/";s:12:"requirements";a:1:{s:13:"app.installer";a:2:{s:7:"version";s:11:">=3.4.0.944";s:6:"strict";b:1;}}s:9:"changelog";a:1:{i:0;a:3:{s:7:"version";s:9:"2.3.3.240";s:7:"content";s:63:"<ul> 
